#, fuzzy
msgid "HQL, JD-QL, Jakarta-QL, Panache-QL"
msgstr "HQL, JD-QL, Jakarta-QL, Panache-QL"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/hibernate-panache-next.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "There are different query languages used in this API:"
msgstr "Existem diferentes linguagens de consulta usadas nesta API:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/hibernate-panache-next.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The link:https://docs.hibernate.org/orm/{hibernate-orm-version-major-minor}/querylanguage/html_single/[Hibernate Query Language] (HQL),\n"
"which is the query language used by Hibernate, supported by the `@HQL` annotation."
msgstr "A link:https://docs.hibernate.org/orm/{hibernate-orm-version-major-minor}/querylanguage/html_single/[Hibernate Query Language] (HQL), que é a linguagem de consulta utilizada pelo Hibernate, suportada pela anotação `@HQL`."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/hibernate-panache-next.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The link:{jakarta-persistence-spec-url}#a4665[Jakarta Persistence Query Language] (JP-QL), which is a subset of the Hibernate\n"
"Query Language. It is currently being moved to its own spec called\n"
"link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/query/1.0/jakarta-query-1.0-m1[Jakarta Query]."
msgstr "A link:{jakarta-persistence-spec-url}#a4665[Jakarta Persistence Query Language] (JP-QL), que é um subconjunto da Hibernate Query Language. Atualmente, ela está sendo movida para sua própria especificação chamada link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/query/1.0/jakarta-query-1.0-m1[Jakarta Query]."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/hibernate-panache-next.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The link:{jakarta-data-spec-url}#_jakarta_data_query_language[Jakarta Data Query Language] (JD-QL), which is a subset of the\n"
"Jakarta Persistence Query Language, supported by the `@Query` annotation."
msgstr "A link:{jakarta-data-spec-url}#_jakarta_data_query_language[Jakarta Data Query Language] (JD-QL), que é um subconjunto da Jakarta Persistence Query Language, suportada pela anotação `@Query`."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/hibernate-panache-next.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Panache Query Language, which is a superset of the Hibernate Query Language adding very few shortcuts, which\n"
"is supported in all the `PanacheRepository` queries."
msgstr "A Panache Query Language, que é um superconjunto da Hibernate Query Language adicionando poucos atalhos, que é suportada em todas as consultas do `PanacheRepository`."

